    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this demo, you'll play as Dinocop as he arrives at the Cretaceous Hotel, where he's tasked with solving a mysterious, meaty case. You'll begin your investigation by interrogating various dinosaurs and inspecting the kiosks at the Dinosaur Rights Convention.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261900/extras/ff9c0464e8278ee645cab6a8ba8be471.avif?t=1771383839\" width=616 height=269 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Humans had the silly idea of bringing dinosaurs back to life, and ever since, relationships between the two species have been strained. You were created in a laboratory to become the only dinosaur cop. Every day, you ask yourself: are you making the world better for your dino peers, or are you just a tool of human propaganda? The meaty case you'll face today might help you answer your most profound existential dilemma. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A rich and funny story starring a cast of anthropomorphic dinosaurs faced with sociopolitical and personal issues</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A puzzling case set in a day cycle. Uncover secrets scattered through time.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you encounter any bugs, please don’t hesitate to report them on our Discord.</p></li></ul>",
